	Section _04_Middle__
		Section hierarchical__
			Section entrance
				Para role bkmrk02 sid misc.bookmark End-Para
				when-date-is
					Jan 6 use: Insert_section noprokeimenon End-Insert
					Dec 25 use: Insert_section noprokeimenon End-Insert
					otherwise use:
