							Media rid meVE.AposTheotokion.text End-Media
							Hymn rid meVE.AposTheotokion.text @ver media-off End-Hymn
						End-Section
					Wednesday, Friday use:
						when-exists
							rid meVE.AposStavrotheotokion.text use:
								Section stavrotheotokion
									Title sid ti.BothNow<Tdesig>sid ti.Stavrotheotokion</>End-Title
									Title role mode rid meVE.AposStavrotheotokion.mode<Tmelody>rid meVE.AposStavrotheotokion.melody</>End-Title
